{"tid":1368550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人嘅農場都發聲","createTime":"2019-07-26T13:40:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T15:33:30.000Z","uid":242792,"like":137,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"7d4dce106c3c1896a6eeabaf115afd95e17c4c1b","tid":1368550,"uid":242792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:40:42.000Z","msg":"［我幫朋友po的］<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ehFOg13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FehFOg13.png&h=ef70348e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WhdDEfx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWhdDEfx.png&h=5b8f575d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/26/213749_223136229b449ecdaa6ca45de2ae46c1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F26%2F213749_223136229b449ecdaa6ca45de2ae46c1.png&h=ed08e59b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/26/213751_b240f0b4c3828598e913e9247778c459.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F26%2F213751_b240f0b4c3828598e913e9247778c459.png&h=6fd1b9c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/26/213802_88907fda47dac3e9c74b8d4690b0d2b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F26%2F213802_88907fda47dac3e9c74b8d4690b0d2b6.png&h=f72db1a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/26/213813_7bd522ae189f806851d519bf04b23bd3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F26%2F213813_7bd522ae189f806851d519bf04b23bd3.png&h=9af6373e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/26/213835_bab726a5251ee4f71bf6d3e1ae078456.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F26%2F213835_bab726a5251ee4f71bf6d3e1ae078456.png&h=5fc31cc2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/26/213850_f9212532d423dadd8489c84dff0e74c9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F26%2F213850_f9212532d423dadd8489c84dff0e74c9.png&h=9ef1b5ce&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/26/213902_fa5ed99a6924215710dae1e800ddb8d5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F26%2F213902_fa5ed99a6924215710dae1e800ddb8d5.png&h=f2da3ba1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/26/213908_334a5b556d78d37eb4aa2680b2287648.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F26%2F213908_334a5b556d78d37eb4aa2680b2287648.png&h=2828467a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一群環保工作者的聲明<br />\n<br />\n我們選擇以環境教育和保育為事業，是希望建立人類與自然共存的願景。我們期望大家關注保育環境、野生動植物等議題的同時，亦不忘自由、公義等普世價值。<br />\n近年香港政府把持議會專制，屢屢漠視社會、民生以及環境利益，倒行逆施的政策多不勝數。我們目睹法治、選舉及言論自由權利岌岌可危，實感痛心。近月，政府不顧一切推動修訂逃犯條例，激發民怨，終釀成大禍。遺憾的是，以林鄭月娥為首的特區政府，至今仍然冥頑不靈，拒絕回應廣大市民的合理訴求。<br />\n7月21日晚上，西鐵元朗站發生駭人聽聞黑社會襲擊市民事件，惟政府及警方依然意圖淡化事件，迴避警黑合作指責。對於相關領袖官員的無德、無恥、無能，我們不禁要問：香港怎會淪落至此﹖<br />\n我們並不想介入政治，只是當政權已逐漸失去最基礎做人良知時，我們這群仍然熱愛香港的人，已再沒有沉默的空間。<br />\n我們要求特區政府懸崖勒馬，立即回應「獨立調查」、「撤回惡法」、「平反暴動」、「撤銷檢控」、「雙真普選」五點訴求。<br />\n<br />\n#嘉道理農場 #保育自然 #農業 #永續 #好人一世平安 #動植物都平安<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t2019年7月26日"},{"pid":"1bd4cb2c1f73a82d7c15ddd5449668bc00b26457","tid":1368550,"uid":190604,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T13:46:46.000Z","msg":"香港人嘅農場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c68b9cfbea034defe4d8333c07a4fe614644075","tid":1368550,"uid":163915,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:03:57.000Z","msg":"我最支持環保人士！阿魚好波！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64f58c6bf7ea2d85e4ea012b4fecb9dd3f1530e1","tid":1368550,"uid":265829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑警死全家"},{"pid":"a491b928556917a398edb7fc911e0e9abc054f3f","tid":1368550,"uid":106336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:12:12.000Z","msg":"細個好鐘意入去農場睇動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8837826af4c5e879b41f74ed387c227592624aac","tid":1368550,"uid":62924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"好波！香港加油！"},{"pid":"b63b8132782ec6420ffcd66ee875eed6c6dc7c24","tid":1368550,"uid":242792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:24:46.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"66738caa3242fe86caacee2fc4249e3f810ffe22","tid":1368550,"uid":79278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:27:55.000Z","msg":"用泥 幾特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0034e52e8fc73708d829144b8482aaa06ded51f6","tid":1368550,"uid":57309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:31:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276430da8cdb317104c2d3ee3a344f9ecf5f312c","tid":1368550,"uid":66018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:21:21.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"8fa83cd6b3baa61aa5a154a19bbcbc52baffd36d","tid":1368550,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"睇到喊"},{"pid":"c188af5f94ed85bc1f18c898395765fd3cd7ddcf","tid":1368550,"uid":264773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T18:06:10.000Z","msg":